results.title: From the Pages of the X-Men--A New Legend is Born!
Time Loves a Hero
results.description: Bishop leaves the X-Men to track down Fitzroy; Finding his sister in a destitute shape, Bishop is confronted by the Chronotroopers and in the midst of their battle, is flung into the far future where Fitzroy rules.

results.title: Preludes Part 2: Can't You Hear Me Knockin'?
results.description: Close on the heels of Nom's death in the mountains, Bishop and crew run into a group of mutants who live under the mountains who call themselves Morlocks; After the obligatory tussel, the Morlocks agree to help Bish travel through the mountains to Fitzroy's castle; Bishop learns that Trevor has his sister.

results.title: The Chronowar Act 1: Helter Skelter
results.description: With his army sitting at the doors, Bishop sneaks into Chronokeep to open the gates and raise his banner, never knowing that he is leading his people right into Fitzroy's trap; Bishop finds Shard but realizes that her loyalties may lie with his enemy as Fitzroy has begun to transform her back into flesh and blood; Bish and his allies take a sound beating.

results.title: The Chronowar Part 2: At the Mercy of the Chronomancer!
The Chronowar Part 2: Shine on You Crazy Diamond
results.description: Fitzroy lords Bishop's defeat over his fallen captive; But the Kith show up to aid Bishop's army against the Chronotroopers; And Shard tells Link Trevor's plan; And she and Michael help Bishop escape; So as Fitzroy prepares to become a god of time, Bishop shows up to try and thwart his mad plan.

results.title: The Chronowar Part 3: The Day Time Stood Still!
The Chronowar Part 3: Remain in the Light
results.description: Bishop tries to keep Fitzroy from completing his time portal which would transform him into a god of time; Nom arrives to reinforce Bishop's army in its fight against the Chronotroopers; Shard and Bishop make hefty sacrifices to ensure that Fitzroy is beaten for good; The good guys win the day, but Bishop disappears in a time blast.

results.title: At Long Last--Reunited With the X-Men!
...Been a Long Lonely, Lonely, Lonely, Lonely, Lonely Time!
results.description: Bishop returns to the current timeline just in time to get caught up in a battle between Xavier and the ruthless Deathbird.

results.title: Dream's End Part Three
results.description: Mystique and Sabretooth are running wild on Muir Isle and only Bishop, Rogue and Wolverine stand in their way; Mystique has developed a strain of the Legacy Virus that will only kill humans; Moira has discovered a cure for the Virus but is gravely injured.

results.title: It's Death From Above for Bishop; Kith Trilogy part 1
Over the Hills and Far Away
In The Hall of the Mountain King
results.description: Bishop and his team meet with the Kith to make a deal.

results.title: Wolverine (2003) #62
results.description:
“GET (classified)" PART 1 
Writer Jason Aaron (Scalped) and artist Ron Garney (AMAZING SPIDER-MAN) bring you a searing 4-part epilogue to the biggest X-Men Event in a decade. In the searing aftermath of “Messiah CompleX,” Wolverine has just one thing on his mind: revenge. But who is the focus of his rage, and what dark secret does he share with them? And how far over the edge is Wolverine willing to go to get what he wants? 
Parental Advisory…$2.99
